{"tid":1794992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國民党真係痴撚線,有党員可以公然上支那党媒做節目","createTime":"2019-12-23T14:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T14:48:51.000Z","uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02c8eddb07ed6f7a7102c6783f1fbecade9456c4","tid":1794992,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:14:46.000Z","msg":"已經擺明認係支共嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nj32mFO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNj32mFO.jpg&h=81ad99f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年12月18日新黨不分區候選人邱毅12月上中國官媒央視節目，在節目中公布臺灣中科院研發的飛彈數量及詳細部署位置，更嗆總統蔡英文害怕遭「斬首」，荒誕行為讓台灣網友看完都直呼傻眼，痛批「這根本是賣台了吧」。"},{"pid":"713ffbbf5817871331a858f5966292693c24f09f","tid":1794992,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"聯俄容共呢家嘢我哋呢啲正常人唔會識㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}